_sText:
This is my first map.

There are two castles, separated only bo thin moat.
One belongs to T, one to CT.

There are many possible ways to dominate opposing team:
* Fight your way through the moat and opponents' gate
* Climb up on the wall using the ladder and smash defenders
* Climb up the rope and kill enemy's snipers on the tower
* Break the wall and sneak inside

There is also one secret, which will give you big advantage over enemies.
Will you find it? ;)

Good frags!
